### Task Management System API — Manual Test Scenarios
### VS Code REST Client — install "REST Client" extension by Humao
###
### Base URL (change to production URL after deployment)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@contentType = application/json

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HEALTH CHECK
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 1. Health check
GET http://localhost:5000/health


# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AUTH
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 2. Register a new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### 3. Register — duplicate email (expect 409)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### 4. Register — missing fields (expect 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "nope@example.com"
}

###

### 5. Login with correct credentials
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### 6. Login — wrong password (expect 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

###

### 7. Login — non-existent email (expect 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "nobody@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### 8. Get current user (requires auth cookie from login)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me

###

### 9. Get current user — no token (expect 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer invalid_token

###

### 10. Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout


# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# TASKS — CRUD
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 11. Create a task
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Complete project documentation",
  "description": "Write README and API docs",
  "status": "Todo",
  "priority": "High",
  "dueDate": "2026-04-01T00:00:00.000Z"
}

###

### 12. Create a task — missing title (expect 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "description": "No title here",
  "priority": "Low"
}

###

### 13. Get all tasks
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks

###

### 14. Get all tasks — filter by status=Done
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks?status=Done

###

### 15. Get all tasks — filter by priority=High
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks?priority=High

###

### 16. Get all tasks — search by title keyword
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks?search=documentation

###

### 17. Get all tasks — sorted by dueDate ascending
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks?sortBy=dueDate&order=asc

###

### 18. Get all tasks — paginated (page 1, 5 per page)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks?page=1&limit=5

###

### 19. Get all tasks — combined filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks?status=Todo&priority=High&sortBy=createdAt&order=desc&page=1&limit=10

###

### 20. Get task by ID (replace with real ID after creating)
# @name createdTask
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/REPLACE_WITH_TASK_ID

###

### 21. Get task by invalid ID (expect 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/invalid-id

###

### 22. Update task (PUT)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tasks/REPLACE_WITH_TASK_ID
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Updated documentation title",
  "priority": "Medium",
  "status": "In Progress"
}

###

### 23. Update task status (PATCH)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tasks/REPLACE_WITH_TASK_ID/status
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "Done"
}

###

### 24. Update status — missing status field (expect 400)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tasks/REPLACE_WITH_TASK_ID/status
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{}

###

### 25. Delete task
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tasks/REPLACE_WITH_TASK_ID

###

### 26. Delete non-existent task (expect 404)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tasks/000000000000000000000000


# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ANALYTICS
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 27. Get analytics (requires auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics

###

### 28. Get analytics — no auth (expect 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics
Authorization: Bearer invalid_token


# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 404 HANDLER
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 29. Unknown route (expect 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/unknown-route
